Gorgeous 1920's, 4 bedroom home hidden away in beautiful Wheat Ridge. Centrally located, just minutes from the mountains and all the Applewood area has to offer.
Nestled on 1/3 acre, this home has the feel of seclusion with the luxury of convenience. With NO HOA, the possibilities are endless.
Take advantage of this amazing property before rates get any higher.
